HAHAHAHAHA, man Impudent...I always just kinda ignored most of your posts and the ppl flaming you saying you don't know what you're talking about until I saw this...<br>
<br>
I'm starting to agree with the masses, you really are kinda clueless.<br>
<br>
Pacification is one of the greatest spells we have.<br>
<br>
I can't count how many times I was able to run to the exit in HoT after a wipe using just Pacification.  Saved tons of time/money we would have wasted on a traditional CR (rogue/monk drag or corpse summon).<br>
<br>
Best example of Pacification and it being &quot;useless&quot;:  We're in HoT fighting 1 or 2 mobs.  A roamer is coming around the corner and heading towards us.  I paci the roamer and it walks right through us in the middle of the fight.  No agro or anything.<br>
<br>
If you're in a group with no mezzer, Pacification is the greatest pull tool.  Single pull all day long.<br>
<br>
Really Imp, you should ask around about how to use your spells before you proclaim them as useless.  You'll find a greater love for your spellbook. <p><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://home.houston.rr.com/danday/gaeaan/compsig.jpg"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
